OL,3,CDrug-related deaths in Scotland remain
OL,4,Chighest in Europe
OL,6,FScottish drug deaths have risen by 12%
OL,7,Fsince last year and remain the highest
OL,8,Fin Europe, ITV News Correspondent
OL,9,FPeter Smith breaks down the figures
OL,11,FThe number of people who died in
OL,12,FScotland due to drug misuse has
OL,13,Fincreased - and remains the highest
OL,14,Fdeath rate in Europe, according to the
OL,15,Flatest figures released by the
OL,16,FNational Records of Scotland (NRS).
OL,18,FThe figures showed there were 1,172
OL,19,Fpeople who died in drug-related deaths
OL,20,Fin 2023, an increase of 121 - or 12% -
OL,21,Fon the previous year.
