OL,3,CDrug-related deaths in Scotland remain
OL,4,Chighest in Europe
OL,6,FHowever, despite the rise on last
OL,7,Fyear, the new figures represent
OL,8,FScotland's second lowest number of
OL,9,Fdrug-related deaths since 2017.
OL,11,FBack in 2022, some 1,051 people died
OL,12,Fdue to drug misuse, which represented
OL,13,Fthe first significant drop in Scottish
OL,14,Fdrug deaths in a number of years.
OL,16,FNRS said after adjusting for age, the
OL,17,Frate of drug misuse deaths was 4.2
OL,18,Ftimes higher in 2023 than in 2000.
