OL,3,CDrug-related deaths in Scotland remain
OL,4,Chighest in Europe
OL,6,FThe report also found that people in
OL,7,FScotland's most deprived areas were 15
OL,8,Ftimes more likely to die of drug
OL,9,Fmisuse last year than those in the
OL,10,Fleast deprived.
OL,12,FGlasgow and Dundee council areas had
OL,13,Fthe highest rates of drug misuse
OL,14,Fdeaths in 2023 while East Renfrewshire
OL,15,Fand East Dunbartonshire had the lowest.
OL,17,FScotland's Health Secretary Neil Gray
OL,18,Fsaid the figures are "hugely
OL,19,Fconcerning and underline why we will
OL,20,Fcontinue to do all we can to reduce
OL,21,Fharm and deaths caused by drugs."
