OL,6,FIn the wake of the "unwelcome rise" in
OL,7,Fdeaths, Mr Gray added: "We will
OL,8,Fintensify our efforts and are also
OL,9,Fworking hard to respond to the growing
OL,10,Fthreat from highly dangerous, super-
OL,11,Fstrong synthetic opioids like
OL,12,Fnitazenes in an increasingly toxic and
OL,13,Funpredictable drug supply."
