OL,3,CDrug-related deaths in Scotland remain
OL,4,Chighest in Europe
OL,6,FOpioid drugs ` such as heroin and
OL,7,Fmethadone ` were implicated in 80% of
OL,8,Fall drugs deaths last year.
OL,10,FThe figures also showed a 16% rise in
OL,11,Fdrugs deaths among males, with the
OL,12,Fnumber of men who died rising by 113
OL,13,Fto 805 in 2023.
OL,15,FThere were also 367 drug deaths
OL,16,Fregistered involving females, with
OL,17,Fthis up by eight (2%) from the
OL,18,Fprevious year.
