OL,3,CDrug-related deaths in Scotland remain
OL,4,Chighest in Europe
OL,6,FNRS Head of Vital Events Statistics
OL,7,FPhillipa Haxton said: "The rate of
OL,8,Fdrug poisoning deaths in Scotland was
OL,9,Fmore than double the rates of other UK
OL,10,Fcountries in 2022.
OL,12,F"The rate was 2.7 times as high as the
OL,13,Frates for England and Northern
OL,14,FIreland, and 2.1 times as high as the
OL,15,Frate in Wales.
OL,17,F"This is the most recent year that
OL,18,Fdata is available for across the UK.
OL,19,FWhen comparing Scotland and the rest
OL,20,Fof the UK, the drug poisoning
OL,21,Fdefinition should be used."
